data.name: grdList.QuerySQL
data.value: /* Print Layout Query */ SELECT DISTINCT TRUNC(A.DRG_PRN_DATE) JUBSU_DATE , A.DRG_PRN_TIME DRG_PRN_TIME , A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO , A.BUNHO BUNHO , B.SUNAME SUNAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('SEX', B.SEX) SEX , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(A.HOPE_DATE, B.BIRTH,'') AGE , A.RESIDENT RESIDENT , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.RESIDENT, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME , B.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.HO_DONG1, A.ORDER_DATE) HO_DONG_NAME , B.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE , B.PKINP1001 PKINP1001 , DECODE( B.TOIWON_RES_DATE , NULL , 'N' , 'Y' ) TOIWON_YN --, A.GWA GWA , '' GWA , A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE , A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE , CASE --WHEN A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' -- AND C.ORDER_GUBUN NOT LIKE '1%' THEN 'ER' --緊急 WHEN A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN LIKE '1%' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') THEN 'P1' --指薬 WHEN A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN LIKE '1%' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('4') THEN 'P2' --指注 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') THEN '21' --臨薬 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' THEN '22' --臨注 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') THEN '31' --退薬 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' THEN '32' --退注 END MAGAM_GUBUN , DECODE( A.BUNRYU1 , '4' , 'Y' , 'N' ) JUSA_YN , DECODE( A.BUNRYU1 , '4' , FN_DRG_GET_MIX_DATE(A.HOSP_CODE, A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO) , '' ) CHULGO_DATE FROM OCS2003 C , VW_OCS_INP1001_01 B , DRG3010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho || '%' AND B.HO_DONG1 LIKE :f_ho_dong || '%' AND TRUNC(A.DRG_PRN_DATE) BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND (:f_magam_gubun = '%' AND (NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' OR NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N') OR :f_magam_gubun = '21' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN NOT LIKE '1%' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --臨薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = '22' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN NOT LIKE '1%' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --臨注 OR :f_magam_gubun = '31' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --退薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = '32' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --退注 OR :f_magam_gubun = 'P1' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN LIKE '1%' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --指薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = 'P2' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN LIKE '1%' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --指注 --OR :f_magam_gubun = 'ER' AND C.ORDER_GUBUN NOT LIKE '1%' AND A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' --緊急 ) AND NVL(DRG_PRN_YN , 'N') = 'Y' --AND NVL(CHULGO_YN , 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.DC_YN , 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN , 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN , 'N') = 'N' --AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN , 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.NALSU , 0 ) > 0 AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 ORDER BY MAGAM_GUBUN, TRUNC(A.DRG_PRN_DATE) DESC, A.DRG_PRN_TIME DESC, HO_DONG, HO_CODE

NVL(A.TOIWON_DRG_YN,'N') = 'N' -- OR :f_toiwon_yn = 'Y' AND NVL(A.TOIWON_DRG_YN,'N') <> 'N') AND (:f_magam_gubun = '%' AND (NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' OR NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N') OR :f_magam_gubun = '21' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --臨薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = '22' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --臨注 OR :f_magam_gubun = '31' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --退薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = '32' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --退注 --OR :f_magam_gubun = 'ER' AND A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' --退注 ) AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL --AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.JAERYO_CODE = A.JAERYO_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND F.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 AND F.HOSP_CODE = G.HOSP_CODE AND F.HANGMOG_CODE = G.HANGMOG_CODE AND F.ORDER_GUBUN NOT LIKE '1%' -- 指示事項除外 AND A.HOPE_DATE BETWEEN G.START_DATE AND G.END_DATE ORDER BY 1,31,2,25,3

data.name: grdMagamJUSAOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,SUBSTR(A.GROUP_SER,2,2) GROUP_SER ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,B.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,CASE WHEN A.NALSU < 0 THEN '-'||CASE WHEN ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) < 1 THEN '0'||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) ELSE ''||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) END ELSE ''||CASE WHEN ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) < 1 THEN '0'||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) ELSE ''||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) END END ORD_SURYANG ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DV DV ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.ORDER_DANUI ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) DANUI_NAME ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,A.BOGYONG_CODE || ' ' || FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN',NVL(A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN,'0')) BOGYONG_NAME ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN ,A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA',NVL(A.JUSA,'0')) JUSA_NAME ,D.SUNAME SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.BANNAB_YN BANNAB_YN ,NVL(A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003,A.FKOCS2003) SOURCE_FKOCS2003 ,A.FKOCS2003 FKOCS2003 ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,A.DC_YN DC_YN ,F.ORDER_GUBUN ORDER_GUBUN ,F.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP ,F.BROUGHT_DRG_YN BROUGHT_DRG_YN ,A.EMERGENCY FROM OCS2003 F, OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE TRUNC(A.DRG_PRN_DATE) = :f_jubsu_date AND A.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('4') --AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' --AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.FKOCS2003 = F.PKOCS2003 ORDER BY 1 DESC, 31 DESC, 2, 29, 30, 4

data.value: SELECT '%' BUSEO_CODE , '全体' BUSEO_NAME FROM DUAL UNION SELECT A.BUSEO_CODE ,A.BUSEO_NAME FROM VW_GWA_NAME A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE AND A.BUSEO_GUBUN = '2' ORDER BY BUSEO_CODE

data.value: /* PRN Not Print Layout Query */ SELECT DISTINCT A.BUNHO BUNHO , B.SUNAME SUNAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('SEX', B.SEX) SEX , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(A.HOPE_DATE, B.BIRTH,'') AGE , A.RESIDENT RESIDENT , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.RESIDENT, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME , '' MAGAM_YN , B.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.HO_DONG1, A.ORDER_DATE) HO_DONG_NAME , B.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE , '' JUNINP_YN , A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE , A.HOPE_TIME HOPE_TIME , B.PKINP1001 PKINP1001 , DECODE( B.TOIWON_RES_DATE , NULL , 'N' , 'Y' ) TOIWON_YN , A.GWA GWA , A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE , A.EMERGENCY EMERGENCY , DECODE( A.BUNRYU1 , '4' , 'P2' , 'P1' ) MAGAM_GUBUN , DECODE( A.BUNRYU1 , '4' , 'Y' , 'N' ) JUSA_YN FROM OCS2003 C , VW_OCS_INP1001_01 B , DRG3010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code --AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho || '%' AND B.HO_DONG1 LIKE :f_ho_dong || '%' AND A.HOPE_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND NVL(DRG_PRN_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(CHULGO_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.DC_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.NALSU, 0 ) > 0 AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 AND C.ORDER_GUBUN LIKE '1%' -- 指示事項 ORDER BY MAGAM_GUBUN, HOPE_DATE DESC, HOPE_TIME, HO_DONG, HO_CODE

A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') THEN '21' --臨薬 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) = 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' THEN '22' --臨注 WHEN NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') THEN '31' --退薬 , DRG3010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho || '%' AND B.HO_DONG1 LIKE :f_ho_dong || '%' AND A.HOPE_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND (:f_magam_gubun = '%' AND , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1', '6') --退薬 OR :f_magam_gubun = '32' AND NVL(A.APPEND_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL( A.TOIWON_DRG_YN , 'N' ) <> 'N' AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' --退注 --OR :f_magam_gubun = 'ER' AND A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' --退注 ) AND NVL(DRG_PRN_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(CHULGO_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.DC_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS data.name: layOutOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'Y' OUTORDER FROM DRG9041 C ,OCS1003 B ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_from_date) AND TO_DATE(:f_to_date) AND A.GWA LIKE NVL(:f_gwa,'%') AND :f_bunho IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'N') = :f_wonyoi_yn AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'N') OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'Y') OR (:f_gubun = '3')) AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND A.FKOCS1003 = B.PKOCS1003 AND SUBSTR(B.ORDER_GUBUN,2,1) IN('C','D') -- C:내복약, D:외용약만 가지고 온다. GROUP BY A.BUNHO, A.ORDER_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y') UNION ALL SELECT 'Y' OUTORDER FROM DRG9041 C ,OCS1003 B ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'N') = :f_wonyoi_yn AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'N') OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'Y') OR (:f_gubun = '3')) AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND A.FKOCS1003 = B.PKOCS1003 AND SUBSTR(B.ORDER_GUBUN,2,1) IN('C','D') -- C:내복약, D:외용약만 가지고 온다. GROUP BY A.BUNHO, A.ORDER_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y')

data.value: SELECT A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,SUBSTR(A.GROUP_SER,2,2) GROUP_SER ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,B.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,CASE WHEN A.NALSU < 0 THEN '-'||CASE WHEN ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) < 1 THEN '0'||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) ELSE ''||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) END ELSE ''||CASE WHEN ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) < 1 THEN '0'||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) ELSE ''||ROUND(A.ORD_SURYANG,2) END END ORD_SURYANG ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DV DV ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.ORDER_DANUI ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) DANUI_NAME ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,C.BOGYONG_NAME BOGYONG_NAME ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN ,A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,A.JUSA JUSA ,D.SUNAME SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.BANNAB_YN BANNAB_YN ,NVL(A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003,A.FKOCS2003) SOURCE_FKOCS2003 ,A.FKOCS2003 FKOCS2003 ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,A.DC_YN DC_YN ,F.ORDER_GUBUN ORDER_GUBUN ,F.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP ,A.RE_USE_YN RE_USE_YN ,F.BROUGHT_DRG_YN BROUGHT_DRG_YN ,A.EMERGENCY FROM OCS2003 F, OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.JUBSU_DATE = :f_jubsu_date AND A.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNRYU1 IN ('1','6') --AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' --AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 ORDER BY 1 DESC, 32 DESC, 2, 29, 30, 4
